tes have a choice of a sport inspired tee or a tank, and either \\\"a stone coloured chino short or a green and gold ombre pleated skirt\\\".\", \"from\": 1712, \"to\": 1882, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the blazer\", \"from\": 1723, \"to\": 1733}, {\"ngram\": \"female athletes\", \"from\": 1735, \"to\": 1750}, {\"ngram\": \"a choice\", \"from\": 1756, \"to\": 1764}, {\"ngram\": \"a sport inspired tee\", \"from\": 1768, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"a tank\", \"from\": 1792, \"to\": 1798}, {\"ngram\": \"a green and gold ombre pleated skirt\", \"from\": 1844, \"to\": 1880}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Male athletes can opt for \\\"a sports inspired tee of their own, with the stretch chino short\\\".\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1977, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Male athletes\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1897}, {\"ngram\": \"a sports inspired tee\", \"from\": 1911, \"to\": 1932}, {\"ngram\": \"the stretch chino\", \"from\": 1952, \"to\": 1969}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The uniform - which will be on show as the opening ceremony takes place along the Seine river on July 26 - is said to be \\\"inspired by the unmistakable essence of Paris\\\".\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 2148, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2061, \"end\": 2066, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 0.9999996132801992, \"rank\": 3.8502216717451114e-07, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}, {\"begin\": 2141, \"end\": 2146, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999595275, \"rank\": 4.0535528240614665e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The uniform\", \"from\": 1979, \"to\": 1990}, {\"ngram\": \"show\", \"from\": 2010, \"to\": 2014}, {\"ngram\": \"the opening cere